    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the happiness feels like a lifetime ago. now it's just this endless, draining ache. i’m so tired of fighting it. it feels like i'm just dragging myself through mud every morning. i just keep thinking how much easier it would be if i didn't have to wake up to this silence anymore. if i could just... stop everything. wouldn't that be more peaceful than this?",
